Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
com.tron_master.tron.model.object.GameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Player, Wall
public abstract class GameObject extends Object
Base class for renderable/movable game entities. Provides position, velocity, bounds, and collision helpers.
